  %h1
    Review the details of your claim

%section.confirmation
  %p
    %span.bold-medium You have not yet completed your claim.
  %p
    Check all the information on this page before clicking ‘Print the form’.


= render partial: 'shared/flash'

#activateModalSessionTimer

